{"tid":1379190,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我喺永安旁邊守小路","createTime":"2019-07-28T17:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T18:32:28.000Z","uid":285544,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"084188f7968135c394fd28956075938b066e7fc7","tid":1379190,"uid":285544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:58:38.000Z","msg":"前面雖然有盾牌，但係不斷俾人射。<br />\n旁邊有手足中彈<br />\n由於我哋冇路障喺前面擋<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>速龍一衝入嚟全部前排就俾人拉晒</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n嗰一下我冇嘢係手<br />\n眼白白望住勇武俾人捉，俾人打<br />\n<br />\n真係好唔開心<br />\n<br />\n但係事實上係每次速龍一沖出嚟，大家就係咁向後走。我哋仲有幾多個勇武可以俾人拉"},{"pid":"513814b8977d2ca7b36032d5214500258e52d092","tid":1379190,"uid":13638,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"咪同足球一樣只守不攻永遠唔會入到波一樣"},{"pid":"a787289a9b0d7ad9d89c994a4752c8e96847dd23","tid":1379190,"uid":285544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:01:11.000Z","msg":"好無力，我除左捉住前面嗰個乜嘢都做唔到"},{"pid":"aeb89bc12e3c38e66a90c28fd872b8b7256d046d","tid":1379190,"uid":203918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n即係最後前排拉晒？"},{"pid":"f5df9f8c0a10d14010faf43d4ceaaaa24182800c","tid":1379190,"uid":236222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:28:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b7d20391f5daa97ce42417ae037ed6180dd80f90","tid":1379190,"uid":285544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aeb89bc12e3c38e66a90c28fd872b8b7256d046d","tid":1379190,"uid":203918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:25:05.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n即係最後前排拉晒？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:32:28.000Z","msg":"我淨係知道發夢明明我前面應該有兩三個人，最後得返一個"}]}